snippet.title: Sker Ritual - Exclusive 'Meet the Elites' Trailer
snippet.description:
Meet the terrifying Mariner, Banshee, Phantom, and Blazeslinger Elites in this exclusive Sker Ritual trailer. Sker Ritual is the spiritual successor to the award-winning horror game, Maid of Sker. Play solo or up to four players as you try to survive the supernatural onslaught of the Quiet Ones in this round-based co-op survival first-person shooter.

Sker Ritual is coming to Steam Early Access in October 2022, followed by its 1.0 PC, PS5, Xbox Series X/S, PS4, and Xbox One launch in Q1 2023. It's available to wishlist on Steam now.

#IGN #Gaming #SkerRitual
